sentences: I bought a Living Social deal $30 for $60 awhile back.
Large selection of dishes for under $9 and there is tons of food.
This particular location has a good check in deal.
Too many other places to shop with better prices.
Today we waited over ten minutes behind one car in the drive thru for their single order
The only problem we really had was the ladies at the front office were sorta rude and looked annoyed at us.
Give me a good waiter and decent food and it's hard to not impress.
needless to say whomever told me this , is a genius .
the waiter was friendly and helpful
I cannot believe someone was not satisfied with the quality of the chicken at this location!
